            <p>The North Shore of Oahu is generally a geographic area between West Oahu's Ka'ena Point and East Oahu's Kahuku Point. The North Shore is very famous for its huge waves during the winter and outstanding coastlines, which attract surfers from around the world. Some favorite North Shore surf spots include Waimea Bay, Sunset Beach, and Banzai Pipeline. </p>

